      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Al Nowfaly, from Al Sakuny, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Rasool-Allah<sup>saww</sup> said; ‘Establishment of the Limit (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>) is better than the rain of forty mornings’."
